    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Welcome to GibblePETS!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>GibblePETS</strong> is a <i>cozy</i> monster collector game where you... collect pets!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will find a <strong>box once every 90 minutes!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090790/extras/95654de1a7eb4c5aa5da0ce6d90992a8.avif?t=1747935731\" width=64 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Opening the box will grant you a pet of a selected rarity with the given chances*:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Common          50%</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncommon      32,95%</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rare                 10%</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Epic                  5%</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mythic              2%</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Legendary        0.05%</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Find your favourite combination!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The unboxed pet will also have an additional 1/10 chance* of having <strong>a special trait!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090790/extras/4fb38fb4f3a1340da642c5c0a9eebbc9.avif?t=1747935731\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090790/extras_big/4fb38fb4f3a1340da642c5c0a9eebbc9.avif?t=1747935731 width=800 height=406 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create special accessories by merging pets and customize them!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090790/extras/359141fa6f86f32aad12d27db588bdf8.avif?t=1747935731\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090790/extras_big/359141fa6f86f32aad12d27db588bdf8.avif?t=1747935731 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090790/extras/1872500d9af67a4f512e0a4fcf40812b.poster.avif?t=1747935731\" width=196 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090790/extras/1872500d9af67a4f512e0a4fcf40812b.webm?t=1747935731\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090790/extras/1872500d9af67a4f512e0a4fcf40812b.mp4?t=1747935731\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>*CHANCES MAY CHANGE WITH TIME!</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customize your pet room!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >have fun customizing the pet's room to your liking, adding items, furnitures and even wallpapers!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090790/extras/8584a4a29716050b2e7dab4340a581e4.avif?t=1747935731\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090790/extras_big/8584a4a29716050b2e7dab4340a581e4.avif?t=1747935731 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Let them stay on your screen!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >GibblePETS can stay on your screen while you keep doing other things to keep you company!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090790/extras/216fa344d12a229a7dfebbb24dfe259b.poster.avif?t=1747935731\" width=800 height=508 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090790/extras/216fa344d12a229a7dfebbb24dfe259b.webm?t=1747935731\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090790/extras/216fa344d12a229a7dfebbb24dfe259b.mp4?t=1747935731\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stay tuned for more updates :)</p>",
